因經營不善，咖啡室於兩年後結業。<br />\n其後他再以相同方式集資開設台式餐廳，最終亦殊途同歸，執笠收場。有網民質疑由始至終是騙局，但被他否認。<br />\n2011年，鍾詠淵以獨立人士身份，參加深水埗麗閣選區區議會選舉，挑戰民協主席馮檢基，但僅得75票慘敗落選。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ccb8ca2538725bd505b4a16243ed67a9e1954b3","tid":1244855,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6e147261ff955674e29ce7e0d742adf75cc213","tid":1244855,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e1e96f0a21faa5a192dfc05c1a2a7604164d23","tid":1244855,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ccbabfc3631f7ae134e894f76e6627a2edaf8d8","tid":1244855,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:55:53.000Z","msg":"又有新野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LWJF6UE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLWJF6UE.png&h=ef6a5dc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XY4J4Gq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXY4J4Gq.png&h=2ab7c566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F6RHAOa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF6RHAOa.png&h=e61d0e27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hy3bt8f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHy3bt8f.png&h=70620674&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed19f36bf4e3456070a0d0170deebeec9b41577b","tid":1244855,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:02:33.000Z","msg":"佢條女都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif